reviewText: These were fantastic and so wonderful to see my 2nd Dad on film again and in this film as an actor as well as stuntman. I have known the family since the late 1940's and his daughter & I are the best of friends to this day.

Old grainey video. Very little Canutt in one of the DVD's.
I would suggest that one should NOT purchase this set. My wife, and I were very unhappy with this set.
